{"tid":2057111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：港府將派「觀察員」列席國泰董事會會議","createTime":"2020-06-09T07:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T09:02:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ab162a1fecb11d386924a0a95804fffbb55125c4","tid":2057111,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"消息：港府將派觀察員列席國泰董事會會議<br />\n09.06.2020 14:54<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空公布，將會集資390億元，政府將提供近300億元財政支持，其中國泰將會向香港政府成立的公司，發行優先股，認購金額195億元，並會發行可認購股份的認股權證，總行使價19.5億元，政府亦會向國泰提供78億已承擔過渡貸款融資，雙方今日已簽訂協議。政府成立的公司，將會持有6%國泰股份，成為國泰第4大股東，消息指，港府將會派觀察員列席國泰董事會會議，保障政府投入的權益。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國泰亦會折讓47%供股，以4.68元供股認購價，每11股供7股，集資金額117億元。國泰表示，受新型冠狀病毒疫情影響，今年首4個月，客運收入下跌至只有去年的約1%，意味國泰自今二月以來，每月虧損25至30億港元。董事局計劃短期內實施新一輪高層減薪，以及第二輪員工自願性無薪假計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1304310&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1304310%26csid%3D261_341&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=cbce216a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1304310&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b7487ecfee1ff7db22331b026b439a3bc16fd1cf","tid":2057111,"uid":226421,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"黨企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5f472b446f5a2fb25a6cc756968979c0a62aff","tid":2057111,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7487ecfee1ff7db22331b026b439a3bc16fd1cf","tid":2057111,"uid":226421,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"黨企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets